used in the paper.\
\>", "Subtitle",ExpressionUUID->"2ffce04a-5b3f-4916-b679-2fcc264afe63"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"ARtri\[Xi]30Rotated", "[", 
